{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.1","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:1","prev_osis_id":"Deut.021.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.022.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Les animaux et les objets \u00e9gar\u00e9s<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-4: cf. (Ex 23:4, 5. Mt 7:12.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.22.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Si tu vois s\u2019\u00e9garer le b\u0153uf ou la brebis de ton fr\u00e8re, tu ne t\u2019en d\u00e9tourneras point, tu les ram\u00e8neras \u00e0 ton fr\u00e8re.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.22","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.2","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:2","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.21.23","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 21:23","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.21.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.2","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:2","prev_osis_id":"Deut.022.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.022.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.22.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Si ton fr\u00e8re n\u2019habite pas pr\u00e8s de toi, et que tu ne le connaisses pas, tu recueilleras l\u2019animal dans ta maison et il restera chez toi jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce que ton fr\u00e8re le r\u00e9clame; et alors tu le lui rendras.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.22","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.3","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:3","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.1","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:1","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.3","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:3","prev_osis_id":"Deut.022.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.022.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.22.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Tu feras de m\u00eame pour son \u00e2ne, tu feras de m\u00eame pour son v\u00eatement, tu feras de m\u00eame pour tout objet qu\u2019il aurait perdu et que tu trouverais; tu ne devras point t\u2019en d\u00e9tourner.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.22","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.2","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:2","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.4","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:4","prev_osis_id":"Deut.022.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.022.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.22.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Si tu vois l\u2019\u00e2ne de ton fr\u00e8re ou son b\u0153uf tomb\u00e9 dans le chemin, tu ne t\u2019en d\u00e9tourneras point, tu l\u2019aideras \u00e0 le relever.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.22","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.5","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:5","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.3","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:3","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.5","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:5","prev_osis_id":"Deut.022.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.022.006,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Les travestissements. Les nids d\u2019oiseaux. Les maisons neuves. Le m\u00e9lange dans les semences et dans les tissus<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 5-12: cf. (L\u00e9 22:27, 28; 19:19. No 15:38-40.) 1 Co 14:33, 40.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.22.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Une femme ne portera point un habillement d\u2019homme, et un homme ne mettra point des v\u00eatements de femme; car quiconque fait ces choses est en abomination \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel, ton Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.22","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.6","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:6","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.6","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:6","prev_osis_id":"Deut.022.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.022.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.22.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Si tu rencontres dans ton chemin un nid d\u2019oiseau, sur un arbre ou sur la terre, avec des petits ou des \u0153ufs, et la m\u00e8re couch\u00e9e sur les petits ou sur les \u0153ufs, tu ne prendras pas la m\u00e8re et les petits,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.22","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.7","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:7","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.5","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:5","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.7","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:7","prev_osis_id":"Deut.022.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.022.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.22.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>tu laisseras aller la m\u00e8re et tu ne prendras que les petits, afin que tu sois heureux et que tu prolonges tes jours.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.22","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.8","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:8","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.6","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:6","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.8","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:8","prev_osis_id":"Deut.022.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.022.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.22.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Si tu b\u00e2tis une maison neuve, tu feras une balustrade autour de ton toit, afin de ne pas mettre du sang sur ta maison, dans le cas o\u00f9 il en tomberait quelqu\u2019un.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.22","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.9","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:9","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.7","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:7","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.9","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:9","prev_osis_id":"Deut.022.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.022.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.22.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Tu ne s\u00e8meras point dans ta vigne diverses semences, de peur que tu ne jouisses ni du produit de ce que tu auras sem\u00e9 ni du produit de la vigne.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.22","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.10","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:10","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.8","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:8","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.10","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:10","prev_osis_id":"Deut.022.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.022.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.22.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Tu ne laboureras point avec un b\u0153uf et un \u00e2ne attel\u00e9s ensemble.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.22","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.11","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:11","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.9","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:9","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.11","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:11","prev_osis_id":"Deut.022.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.022.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.22.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Tu ne porteras point un v\u00eatement tiss\u00e9 de diverses esp\u00e8ces de fils, de laine et de lin r\u00e9unis ensemble.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.22","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.12","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:12","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.10","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:10","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.12","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:12","prev_osis_id":"Deut.022.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.022.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.22.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Tu mettras des franges aux quatre coins du v\u00eatement dont tu te couvriras.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.22","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.13","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:13","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.11","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:11","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.13","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:13","prev_osis_id":"Deut.022.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.022.014,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 13-21: cf. No 5:11-31.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.22.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Si un homme, qui a pris une femme et est all\u00e9 vers elle, \u00e9prouve ensuite de l\u2019aversion pour sa personne,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.22","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.14","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:14","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.12","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:12","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.14","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:14","prev_osis_id":"Deut.022.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.022.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.22.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>s\u2019il lui impute des choses criminelles et porte atteinte \u00e0 sa r\u00e9putation, en disant: J\u2019ai pris cette femme, je me suis approch\u00e9 d\u2019elle, et je ne l\u2019ai pas trouv\u00e9e vierge,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.22","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.15","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:15","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.13","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:13","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.15","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:15","prev_osis_id":"Deut.022.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.022.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.22.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>alors le p\u00e8re et la m\u00e8re de la jeune femme prendront les signes de sa virginit\u00e9 et les produiront devant les anciens de la ville, \u00e0 la porte.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.22","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.16","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:16","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.14","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:14","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.16","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:16","prev_osis_id":"Deut.022.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.022.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.22.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Le p\u00e8re de la jeune femme dira aux anciens: J\u2019ai donn\u00e9 ma fille pour femme \u00e0 cet homme, et il l\u2019a prise en aversion;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.22","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.17","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:17","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.15","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:15","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.17","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:17","prev_osis_id":"Deut.022.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.022.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.22.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>il lui impute des choses criminelles, en disant: Je n\u2019ai pas trouv\u00e9 ta fille vierge. Or voici les signes de virginit\u00e9 de ma fille. Et ils d\u00e9ploieront son v\u00eatement devant les anciens de la ville.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.22","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.18","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:18","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.16","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:16","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.18","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:18","prev_osis_id":"Deut.022.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.022.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.22.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Les anciens de la ville saisiront alors cet homme et le ch\u00e2tieront;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.22","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.19","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:19","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.17","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:17","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.19","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:19","prev_osis_id":"Deut.022.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.022.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.22.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>et, parce qu\u2019il a port\u00e9 atteinte \u00e0 la r\u00e9putation d\u2019une vierge d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, ils le condamneront \u00e0 une amende de cent sicles d\u2019argent, qu\u2019ils donneront au p\u00e8re de la jeune femme. Elle restera sa femme, et il ne pourra pas la renvoyer, tant qu\u2019il vivra.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.22","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.20","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:20","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.18","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:18","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.20","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:20","prev_osis_id":"Deut.022.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.022.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.22.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Mais si le fait est vrai, si la jeune femme ne s\u2019est point trouv\u00e9e vierge,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.22","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.21","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:21","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.19","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:19","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.21","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:21","prev_osis_id":"Deut.022.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.022.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.22.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>on fera sortir la jeune femme \u00e0 l\u2019entr\u00e9e de la maison de son p\u00e8re; elle sera lapid\u00e9e par les gens de la ville, et elle mourra, parce qu\u2019elle a commis une infamie en Isra\u00ebl, en se prostituant dans la maison de son p\u00e8re. Tu \u00f4teras ainsi le mal du milieu de toi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.22","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.22","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:22","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.20","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:20","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.22","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:22","prev_osis_id":"Deut.022.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.022.023,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 22-30: cf. L\u00e9 20:10, 11. H\u00e9 13:4. 1 Th 4:3-7.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.22.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>\n    Si l\u2019on trouve un homme couch\u00e9 avec une femme mari\u00e9e, ils mourront tous deux, l\u2019homme qui a couch\u00e9 avec la femme, et la femme aussi. Tu \u00f4teras ainsi le mal du milieu d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.22","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.23","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:23","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.21","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:21","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.23","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:23","prev_osis_id":"Deut.022.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.022.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.22.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Si une jeune fille vierge est fianc\u00e9e, et qu\u2019un homme la rencontre dans la ville et couche avec elle,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.22","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.24","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:24","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.22","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:22","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.24","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:24","prev_osis_id":"Deut.022.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.022.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.22.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>vous les am\u00e8nerez tous deux \u00e0 la porte de la ville, vous les lapiderez, et ils mourront, la jeune fille pour n\u2019avoir pas cri\u00e9 dans la ville, et l\u2019homme pour avoir d\u00e9shonor\u00e9 la femme de son prochain. Tu \u00f4teras ainsi le mal du milieu de toi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.22","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.25","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:25","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.23","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:23","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.25","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:25","prev_osis_id":"Deut.022.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.022.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.22.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Mais si c\u2019est dans les champs que cet homme rencontre la jeune femme fianc\u00e9e, lui fait violence et couche avec elle, l\u2019homme qui aura couch\u00e9 avec elle sera seul puni de mort.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.22","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.26","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:26","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.24","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:24","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.26","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:26","prev_osis_id":"Deut.022.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.022.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.22.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>Tu ne feras rien \u00e0 la jeune fille; elle n\u2019est pas coupable d\u2019un crime digne de mort, car il en est de ce cas comme de celui o\u00f9 un homme se jette sur son prochain et lui \u00f4te la vie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.22","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.27","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:27","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.25","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:25","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.27","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:27","prev_osis_id":"Deut.022.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.022.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.22.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>La jeune fille fianc\u00e9e, que cet homme a rencontr\u00e9e dans les champs, a pu crier sans qu\u2019il y ait eu personne pour la secourir.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.22","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.28","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:28","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.26","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:26","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.28","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:28","prev_osis_id":"Deut.022.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.022.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.22.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>Si un homme rencontre une jeune fille vierge non fianc\u00e9e, lui fait violence et couche avec elle, et qu\u2019on vienne \u00e0 les surprendre,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.22","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.29","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:29","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.27","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:27","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.29","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:29","prev_osis_id":"Deut.022.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.022.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.22.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>l\u2019homme qui aura couch\u00e9 avec elle donnera au p\u00e8re de la jeune fille cinquante sicles d\u2019argent; et, parce qu\u2019il l\u2019a d\u00e9shonor\u00e9e, il la prendra pour femme, et il ne pourra pas la renvoyer, tant qu\u2019il vivra.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.22","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.30","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:30","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.28","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:28","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.30","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:30","prev_osis_id":"Deut.022.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.023.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.22.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup>Nul ne prendra la femme de son p\u00e8re, et ne soul\u00e8vera la couverture de son p\u00e8re.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.22","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.23.1","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 23:1","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.23.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.22.29","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 22:29","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.22.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb709a582.39244325');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb709a582.39244325\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb709a582.39244325","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb709a582.39244325'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb709a582.39244325\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}